{"id": "ChIJa8lV9GZ_hYARjrRJXne-U5A", "rating": 4.7, "userRatingCount": 501, "displayName": {"text": "June's Pizza", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJa8lV9GZ_hYARjrRJXne-U5A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sblZYUnRiWEkyYzBSQ09WWjNVSE5rV1dSblRWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We had such a great time at June's! I love how simple the menu is, only offering three pizzas: margherita, pepperoni, and a rotating seasonal option. The staff were friendly and efficient. They answered my questions about allergens in the dipping sauces. Hooray for tree nut-free pesto! 🎉🍻\n\nThe ambiance was pretty rad too. The space has such tall ceilings that, although the tables are pretty crammed together, it didn't feel very cramped at all. The yellow tile on the pizza oven and the overall aesthetic of the place are really lovely.\n\nThe pizza was absolutely delicious. We particularly enjoyed the seasonal option, which had zucchini, green onion, and some other tasty toppings. The star of the show, though, was the pesto dipping sauce we got on the side.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We had such a great time at June's! I love how simple the menu is, only offering three pizzas: margherita, pepperoni, and a rotating seasonal option. The staff were friendly and efficient. They answered my questions about allergens in the dipping sauces. Hooray for tree nut-free pesto! 🎉🍻\n\nThe ambiance was pretty rad too. The space has such tall ceilings that, although the tables are pretty crammed together, it didn't feel very cramped at all. The yellow tile on the pizza oven and the overall aesthetic of the place are really lovely.\n\nThe pizza was absolutely delicious. We particularly enjoyed the seasonal option, which had zucchini, green onion, and some other tasty toppings. The star of the show, though, was the pesto dipping sauce we got on the side.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sam Myers", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107686363009328911883/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzZ2Zc7--aUD_adrEOixeAj2k0aNG77kBrBoaM03PfW3lBtGSGqA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-02T17:26:26.659277097Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sblZYUnRiWEkyYzBSQ09WWjNVSE5rV1dSblRWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sblZYUnRiWEkyYzBSQ09WWjNVSE5rV1dSblRWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f66f455c96b:0x9053be775e49b48e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJa8lV9GZ_hYARjrRJXne-U5A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGaVdYUlRabUpITWxGMVJuUjZXVXhCTVRScExVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Excellent pizza with an excellent under carriage. Nice charred bit on the crust. They put fresh basil on the cooked pizza with adds a nice herbaceous finish. The sauce has a nice mix of sweet and sour flavors that pairs nicely with the pepperoni. The Parmesan shaved on top is great touch. The inside does have an industrial vibe.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Excellent pizza with an excellent under carriage. Nice charred bit on the crust. They put fresh basil on the cooked pizza with adds a nice herbaceous finish. The sauce has a nice mix of sweet and sour flavors that pairs nicely with the pepperoni. The Parmesan shaved on top is great touch. The inside does have an industrial vibe.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sam Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110081342328282772536/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4WTUeCogVxqibN7gX_nG4MGUmakWDGtqaGJU7qjL5_VgO_mUcbA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-12T15:57:24.010344306Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGaVdYUlRabUpITWxGMVJuUjZXVXhCTVRScExVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGaVdYUlRabUpITWxGMVJuUjZXVXhCTVRScExVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f66f455c96b:0x9053be775e49b48e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJa8lV9GZ_hYARjrRJXne-U5A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RdFNUSjVVM2swVFZGMFEyZGtWV0pqV25WS01tYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Simple menu - if there are no specials you just have the margarita and pepperoni options but it's for good reason bc they do it so well. Highly recommend the wakame Cesar sauce on the side to dip the crust into. Parking spaces are limited and it gets filled up really fast so I'd recommend you come ten minute before opening!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Simple menu - if there are no specials you just have the margarita and pepperoni options but it's for good reason bc they do it so well. Highly recommend the wakame Cesar sauce on the side to dip the crust into. Parking spaces are limited and it gets filled up really fast so I'd recommend you come ten minute before opening!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "raven eats", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100989219977562295309/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGsZsIzhr0hu6aNT-CwUuEBxOi9AXwrD52VKriGM14aUBaRg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-12T00:57:48.171048342Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RdFNUSjVVM2swVFZGMFEyZGtWV0pqV25WS01tYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RdFNUSjVVM2swVFZGMFEyZGtWV0pqV25WS01tYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f66f455c96b:0x9053be775e49b48e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJa8lV9GZ_hYARjrRJXne-U5A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25scVpXbGpkVjlaTFhkUVZuUktNRUptUlZjMlMwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "First time trying this pizza spot after hearing good things. The crust was over charred and left a bitter taste, but the garlic sauce was amazing - nice acidity to it. The pepperoni and cheese were nice quality. The crust just made it hard to enjoy.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "First time trying this pizza spot after hearing good things. The crust was over charred and left a bitter taste, but the garlic sauce was amazing - nice acidity to it. The pepperoni and cheese were nice quality. The crust just made it hard to enjoy.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Bia", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107712725218669759812/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaOq90zuDYRCN-E2F_tfZJ2FkAcTXw92n5LCo72apcHivumBc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-26T05:40:40.611522095Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25scVpXbGpkVjlaTFhkUVZuUktNRUptUlZjMlMwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25scVpXbGpkVjlaTFhkUVZuUktNRUptUlZjMlMwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f66f455c96b:0x9053be775e49b48e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJa8lV9GZ_hYARjrRJXne-U5A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Kb1UxUnJOblZ3TlZBM1ZsSjFXV2gyZG5CUlFuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "So good - the flavor is 10/10. Generous shaving of that cheese on top. Slices were big, a little floppy but with structure and not soaked in grease. Even the chew of their crust was good - didn't feel dry or bland at all. Love that their menu is super simple - 1 veg, 1 pepperoni. you can order a half & half to try both!\n\nNext to a brewery so we go it to go next door and get a beer. Great set up. The wait was 15 mins on a Sat with a decent 5 person line and a full & busy open kitchen. It was good vibes.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "So good - the flavor is 10/10. Generous shaving of that cheese on top. Slices were big, a little floppy but with structure and not soaked in grease. Even the chew of their crust was good - didn't feel dry or bland at all. Love that their menu is super simple - 1 veg, 1 pepperoni. you can order a half & half to try both!\n\nNext to a brewery so we go it to go next door and get a beer. Great set up. The wait was 15 mins on a Sat with a decent 5 person line and a full & busy open kitchen. It was good vibes.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Fei Yu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108526166045051159983/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVv0GnzLwq8PkMoBfjnjwme5vvrEvxkpCVrWTnBT6oX0sEBQao=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-23T04:40:13.927084319Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Kb1UxUnJOblZ3TlZBM1ZsSjFXV2gyZG5CUlFuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Kb1UxUnJOblZ3TlZBM1ZsSjFXV2gyZG5CUlFuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f66f455c96b:0x9053be775e49b48e"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJa8lV9GZ_hYARjrRJXne-U5A/photos/AWCwydj022sprXCzWultrVaHIaL0yFGx_njRr-vM7DZ7xy8TK5HaHD0yPMs2rk-fbPepjhXwFYsHdzcw7tmtDAe9XpB3j41y3iR_vmNiGJsqEriQpLQzwrmhj9HhyU5JTGxKeeY-Uv6Hx3hxt-y97BLOtCNOSHpErrsLdYIlks2nUZQrUw8Fc9QXRPA51UBxrNatUpxg02_WGiaFUvyMf8Pw6XsIu6QxFei-lyaSP85tamH7mpz7w6C6nfSBAyMC228oLmf6v3bnKJL4U1q3sGS5BtlfGbXUwWubw4h593N4nmu2qUOmfc7uC4lffb8j2y81HrFRXLHS3O-ZtGTuKhcSoYaiteDVRmf45GPWyU2xPoCqgwiMsrMjWBTNCISs5wrqfWfxqO7zqpUbHB4S8KVGuUn0MCeyRLOvFip1bAJ8MBfWFcJL", "widthPx": 4032, "heightPx": 3024, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Andrew “jc” Chang", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/111574532729357790876", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5MKPNju2GorK0qGV